    "body": "Here is the sample backing tree of a `Validator` structure: \r\n```\r\n├─┐\r\n│ ├─┐\r\n│ │ ├─┐\r\n│ │ │ ├─[0x8c43edcff6f1d56f2a42072637c0cfd9467ddfccb918ce1a8c2d1babb9cdd658]\r\n│ │ │ └─[0x4b601dde9b2bafe027be489bbdcf82ef00000000000000000000000000000000]\r\n│ │ └─[0x92fcc742102977503966d35cb217fc55bd583232b0c551605c08b9c319485bb5]\r\n│ └─┐\r\n│   ├─[0x0040597307000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000]\r\n│   └─[0x0]\r\n└─┐\r\n  ├─┐\r\n  │ ├─[0xffffffffffffffff000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000]\r\n  │ └─[0xffffffffffffffff000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000]\r\n  └─┐\r\n    ├─[0xffffffffffffffff000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000]\r\n    └─[0xffffffffffffffff000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000]\r\n```\r\n1. All values are stored unpacked\r\n2. `validators` list yields 900K of leaf nodes and ~900K of branch nodes which is almost 97% of all nodes ",
